- Gate report maps each invariant/path to its proving tests for auditability.","notes":"This enforces the project’s real-behavior test philosophy and prevents regression to mock-only confidence.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:24:51.056490827Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T00:04:59.236464660Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.1.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:25:12.814095669Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.2.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:25:13.068455733Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.2.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:25:13.323155864Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.3.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:24:51.056490827Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
