 {"id":"bd-mblr.4","title":"E2E Scenario Completeness","description":"Define and implement a complete end-to-end scenario matrix (DDL/DML/transactions/concurrency/recovery/corruption/compatibility) with deterministic reproducibility and artifact capture.","design":"Scenario completeness should be requirements-traceable, not ad-hoc test accumulation.","acceptance_criteria":"Scenario matrix published with full ownership; missing required scenarios implemented; deterministic replay metadata emitted; failure bundles complete.","notes":"Deferred intentionally for queue hygiene: this bead is a container/coordination umbrella, not a direct implementation lane. Work proceeds through its child tasks; reopen/close this bead during milestone rollup and completion review.","status":"deferred","priority":1,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:23:16.914003853Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T00:51:03.695330127Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:23:16.914003853Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.4","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:25:06.106603431Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":1341,"issue_id":"bd-mblr.4","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"Detailed scope: produce an explicit scenario ledger with owning tests and pass criteria. Completion is defined by closure of matrix gaps, not by raw test count growth. Every required scenario must have deterministic replay data.","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:26:03Z"}]}
